snippet.title: Rock Band Opening Cinematic
snippet.description:
Rock Band's opening cinematic featuring Deep Purple's "Highway Star".
Rock Band ships November 20 on PS3 and Xbox 360 and December 11 on PS2.
http://www.rockband.com
